"propounded, not emancipating, not leading to peace, announced by someone who "
"is not a fully awakened Buddha."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn29:11.1"
msgid "2. Sammāsambuddhappaveditadhammavinaya"
msgstr "The Teaching of the Awakened"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="wp" id="wp8"></a>
