#. id="pts3.125"></a>
msgctxt "dn29:24.1"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, cunda, etehi ceva aṅgehi samannāgataṃ brahmacariyaṃ hoti, "
"satthā ca hoti thero rattaññū cirapabbajito addhagato vayoanuppatto, therā "
"cassa bhikkhū sāvakā honti viyattā vinītā visāradā pattayogakkhemā."
msgstr ""
"But when a spiritual path possesses those factors and the teacher is senior "
"and there are competent senior monks, "

msgctxt "dn29:24.2"
msgid ""
"Alaṃ samakkhātuṃ saddhammassa, alaṃ uppannaṃ parappavādaṃ sahadhammehi "
"suniggahitaṃ niggahetvā sappāṭihāriyaṃ dhammaṃ desetuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn29:24.3"
msgid "Majjhimā cassa bhikkhū sāvakā honti …"
msgstr "middle monks,"

msgctxt "dn29:24.4"
msgid "navā cassa bhikkhū sāvakā honti …"
msgstr "junior monks,"

msgctxt "dn29:24.5"
msgid "therā cassa bhikkhuniyo sāvikā honti …"
msgstr "senior nuns,"

msgctxt "dn29:24.6"
msgid "majjhimā cassa bhikkhuniyo sāvikā honti …"
msgstr "middle nuns,"

msgctxt "dn29:24.7"
msgid "navā cassa bhikkhuniyo sāvikā honti …"
