msgctxt "dn29:24.14"
msgid "Evaṃ taṃ brahmacariyaṃ paripūraṃ hoti tenaṅgena."
msgstr "then that spiritual path is complete in that respect."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="18"></a><a class="wp" id="wp18"></a>
msgctxt "dn29:25.1"
msgid ""
"Ahaṃ kho pana, cunda, etarahi satthā loke uppanno arahaṃ sammāsambuddho."
msgstr ""
"I, Cunda, am a teacher who has arisen in the world today, perfected and "
"fully awakened."

msgctxt "dn29:25.2"
msgid ""
"Dhammo ca svākkhāto suppavedito niyyāniko upasamasaṃvattaniko "
"sammāsambuddhappavedito."
msgstr ""
"The teaching is well explained and well propounded, emancipating, leading to "
"peace, announced by someone who is fully awakened. "

msgctxt "dn29:25.3"
msgid ""
"Viññāpitatthā ca me sāvakā saddhamme, kevalañca tesaṃ paripūraṃ "
"brahmacariyaṃ āvikataṃ uttānīkataṃ sabbasaṅgāhapadakataṃ sappāṭihīrakataṃ "
"yāva devamanussehi suppakāsitaṃ."
msgstr ""
"My disciples have inquired about the meaning of that good teaching. And the "
"spiritual practice that’s entirely full and pure has been disclosed and "
"revealed to them with all its collected sayings, with its demonstrable "
"basis, well proclaimed wherever there are gods and humans."

msgctxt "dn29:25.4"
msgid ""
"Ahaṃ kho pana, cunda, etarahi satthā thero rattaññū cirapabbajito addhagato "
"vayoanuppatto."
msgstr ""
"I am a teacher today who is senior, long standing, long gone forth, advanced "
"in years, and have reached the final stage of life."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="19"></a><a class="wp" id="wp19"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts3.126"></a>
msgctxt "dn29:26.1"
msgid ""
"Santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi therā bhikkhū sāvakā honti viyattā vinītā "
"visāradā pattayogakkhemā."
msgstr "I have today disciples who are competent senior monks,"

msgctxt "dn29:26.2"
msgid ""
"Alaṃ samakkhātuṃ saddhammassa, alaṃ uppannaṃ parappavādaṃ sahadhammehi "
"suniggahitaṃ niggahetvā sappāṭihāriyaṃ dhammaṃ desetuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn29:26.3"
msgid "Santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi majjhimā bhikkhū sāvakā …"
msgstr "middle monks,"

msgctxt "dn29:26.4"
msgid "santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi navā bhikkhū sāvakā …"
msgstr "junior monks,"

msgctxt "dn29:26.5"
msgid "santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi therā bhikkhuniyo sāvikā …"
msgstr "senior nuns,"

msgctxt "dn29:26.6"
msgid "santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi majjhimā bhikkhuniyo sāvikā …"
msgstr "middle nuns,"

msgctxt "dn29:26.7"
msgid "santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi navā bhikkhuniyo sāvikā …"
msgstr "junior nuns,"

msgctxt "dn29:26.8"
msgid ""
"santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi upāsakā sāvakā gihī odātavasanā "
"brahmacārino …"
msgstr "celibate laymen,"

msgctxt "dn29:26.9"
msgid ""
"santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi upāsakā sāvakā gihī odātavasanā "
"kāmabhogino …"
msgstr "laymen enjoying sensual pleasures,"

msgctxt "dn29:26.10"
msgid ""
"santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi upāsikā sāvikā gihiniyo odātavasanā "
"brahmacāriniyo …"
msgstr "celibate laywomen,"

msgctxt "dn29:26.11"
msgid ""
"santi kho pana me, cunda, etarahi upāsikā sāvikā gihiniyo odātavasanā "
"kāmabhoginiyo …"
msgstr "and laywomen enjoying sensual pleasures."

msgctxt "dn29:26.12"
msgid ""
"etarahi kho pana me, cunda, brahmacariyaṃ iddhañceva phītañca vitthārikaṃ "
"bāhujaññaṃ puthubhūtaṃ yāva devamanussehi suppakāsitaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Today my spiritual life is successful and prosperous, extensive, popular, "
"widespread, and well proclaimed wherever there are gods and humans."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="20"></a><a class="wp" id="wp20"></a>
msgctxt "dn29:27.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvatā kho, cunda, etarahi satthāro loke uppannā, nāhaṃ, cunda, aññaṃ "
"ekasatthārampi samanupassāmi evaṃlābhaggayasaggappattaṃ yatharivāhaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Of all the teachers in the world today, Cunda, I don’t see even a single one "
"who has reached the pinnacle of material possessions and fame like me."

msgctxt "dn29:27.2"
msgid "Yāvatā kho pana, cunda, etarahi saṅgho vā gaṇo vā loke uppanno;"
msgstr ""
"Of all the spiritual communities and groups in the world today, Cunda, I don’"
"t see even a single one who has reached the pinnacle of material possessions "
"and fame like the mendicant Saṅgha."

msgctxt "dn29:27.3"
msgid ""
"nāhaṃ, cunda, aññaṃ ekasaṅghampi samanupassāmi evaṃlābhaggayasaggappattaṃ "
"yatharivāyaṃ, cunda, bhikkhusaṅgho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn29:27.4"
msgid "Yaṃ kho taṃ, cunda, sammā vadamāno vadeyya:"
msgstr "And if there’s any spiritual path of which it may be rightly said that"

msgctxt "dn29:27.5"
msgid ""
"‘sabbākārasampannaṃ sabbākāraparipūraṃ anūnamanadhikaṃ svākkhātaṃ kevalaṃ "
"paripūraṃ brahmacariyaṃ suppakāsitan’ti."
