msgid ""
"‘sabbākārasampannaṃ sabbākāraparipūraṃ anūnamanadhikaṃ svākkhātaṃ kevalaṃ "
"paripūraṃ brahmacariyaṃ suppakāsitan’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn29:29.1"
msgid "6. Saṅgāyitabbadhamma"
msgstr "Teachings Should be Recited in Concert"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="22"></a><a class="wp" id="wp22"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts3.128"></a>
msgctxt "dn29:30.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, cunda, ye vo mayā dhammā abhiññā desitā, tattha sabbeheva "
"saṅgamma samāgamma atthena atthaṃ byañjanena byañjanaṃ saṅgāyitabbaṃ na "
"vivaditabbaṃ, yathayidaṃ brahmacariyaṃ addhaniyaṃ assa ciraṭṭhitikaṃ, "
"tadassa bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya "
"devamanussānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"So, Cunda, you should all come together and recite in concert, without "
"disputing, those things I have taught you from my direct knowledge, "
"comparing meaning with meaning and phrasing with phrasing, so that this "
"spiritual path may last for a long time. That would be for the welfare and "
"happiness of many people, for the benefit, welfare, and happiness of gods "
"and humans."

msgctxt "dn29:30.2"
msgid ""
"Katame ca te, cunda, dhammā mayā abhiññā desitā, yattha sabbeheva saṅgamma "
"samāgamma atthena atthaṃ byañjanena byañjanaṃ saṅgāyitabbaṃ na vivaditabbaṃ, "
"yathayidaṃ brahmacariyaṃ addhaniyaṃ assa ciraṭṭhitikaṃ, tadassa "
"bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya atthāya hitāya sukhāya "
"devamanussānaṃ?"
msgstr "And what are those things I have taught from my direct knowledge?"

msgctxt "dn29:30.3"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "They are"

msgctxt "dn29:30.4"
msgid ""
"cattāro satipaṭṭhānā, cattāro sammappadhānā, cattāro iddhipādā, "
"pañcindriyāni, pañca balāni, satta bojjhaṅgā, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo."
msgstr ""
"the four kinds of mindfulness meditation, the four right endeavors, the four "
"bases for psychic power, the five faculties, the five powers, the seven "
"factors of awakening, and the eightfold noble path."

msgctxt "dn29:30.5"
msgid "Ime kho te, cunda, dhammā mayā abhiññā desitā."
msgstr "These are the things I have taught from my own direct knowledge."

msgctxt "dn29:30.6"
msgid ""
"Yattha sabbeheva saṅgamma samāgamma atthena atthaṃ byañjanena byañjanaṃ "
"saṅgāyitabbaṃ na vivaditabbaṃ, yathayidaṃ brahmacariyaṃ addhaniyaṃ assa "
"ciraṭṭhitikaṃ, tadassa bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya atthāya "
"hitāya sukhāya devamanussānaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn29:31.1"
msgid "7. Saññāpetabbavidhi"
msgstr "Reaching Agreement"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="23"></a><a class="wp" id="wp23"></a>
#. VAR: sikkhataṃ → sikkhitabbaṃ (bahūsu)
msgctxt "dn29:32.1"
msgid ""
"Tesañca vo, cunda, samaggānaṃ sammodamānānaṃ avivadamānānaṃ sikkhataṃ "
"aññataro sabrahmacārī saṃghe dhammaṃ bhāseyya."
msgstr ""
"Suppose one of those spiritual companions who is training in harmony and "
"mutual appreciation, without fighting, were to recite the teaching in the "
"Saṅgha."

msgctxt "dn29:32.2"
msgid "Tatra ce tumhākaṃ evamassa:"
msgstr "Now, you might think:"

#. VAR: ceva → yo ceva (s1-3, pts1) | yañceva (mr)
msgctxt "dn29:32.3"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ kho āyasmā atthañceva micchā gaṇhāti, byañjanāni ca micchā ropetī’ti."
msgstr "‘This venerable misconstrues the meaning and mistakes the phrasing.’"

msgctxt "dn29:32.4"
msgid ""
"Tassa neva abhinanditabbaṃ na paṭikkositabbaṃ, anabhinanditvā appaṭikkositvā "
"so evamassa vacanīyo:"
msgstr "You should neither approve nor dismiss them, but say:"

#. VAR: imesañca → imesaṃ (sabbattha)
msgctxt "dn29:32.5"
msgid ""
"‘imassa nu kho, āvuso, atthassa imāni vā byañjanāni etāni vā byañjanāni "
"katamāni opāyikatarāni, imesañca byañjanānaṃ ayaṃ vā attho eso vā attho "
"katamo opāyikataro’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Reverend, if this is the meaning, the phrasing may either be this or that: "
"which is more fitting? And if this is the phrasing, the meaning may be "
"either this or that: which is more fitting?’"

msgctxt "dn29:32.6"
msgid "So ce evaṃ vadeyya:"
msgstr "Suppose they reply:"

msgctxt "dn29:32.7"
msgid ""
"‘imassa kho, āvuso, atthassa imāneva byañjanāni opāyikatarāni, yā ceva etāni;"
msgstr ""
"‘This phrasing fits the meaning better than that. And this meaning fits the "
"phrasing better than that.’"

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn29:32.8"
msgid "imesañca byañjanānaṃ ayameva attho opāyikataro, yā ceva eso’ti."
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn29:32.9"
msgid ""
"So neva ussādetabbo na apasādetabbo, anussādetvā anapasādetvā sveva sādhukaṃ "
"saññāpetabbo tassa ca atthassa tesañca byañjanānaṃ nisantiyā."
msgstr ""
"Without flattering or rebuking them, you should carefully convince them by "
"examining that meaning and that phrasing."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="24"></a><a class="wp" id="wp24"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts3.129"></a>
msgctxt "dn29:33.1"
msgid "Aparopi ce, cunda, sabrahmacārī saṅghe dhammaṃ bhāseyya."
